# Production build config (loaded automatically by `vite build`).
#
# Same-origin: the deploy fronts the SPA and the agent API behind one reverse
# proxy (see Caddyfile), so the UI calls /v1/* on its own origin. A non-empty
# value here selects the live HTTP adapter; leaving it unset would fall back to
# the in-browser MOCK adapter — which must never happen for a production bundle.
# `/` is normalized to an empty base in createApi(), i.e. same-origin requests.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=/
